<br>
I dont buy CD's to support musicians - I am buying the CD for the sheer convenience of having it on a handy disc ready to play, nicely packaged etc.<br>
<br>
I'm not going to stop downloading mp3's. Regardless of what the law says, I think I am perfectly entitled to download music. If artists dont want me to hear their music, they should stop producing it.<br>
<br>
<br>
Dash<br>
